\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {10}{\ignorespaces The real-time player dashboard. The left panel tracks the event log, the center maps directed actions, and the right exposes the agent's internal cognitive models. If interactions are needed, a fourth panel, centered on the bottom, appears and dictates what to do.}}{31}{figure.caption.24}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:ui_dashboard}{{10}{31}{The real-time player dashboard. The left panel tracks the event log, the center maps directed actions, and the right exposes the agent's internal cognitive models. If interactions are needed, a fourth panel, centered on the bottom, appears and dictates what to do}{figure.caption.24}{}}
